</P>
<P>
Sezgin was assuring the Arab countries in an interview with a
Kuwaiti newspaper published today.
</P>
<P>
He was speaking to correct a Turkish foreign ministry spokesman
who confirmed Friday a joint operation by Turkish and Israeli
naval forces in the eastern Mediterranean scheduled for October.
</P>
