stability in the Middle East, adding that his country would not
accept any foreign interference in the Middle East issues.
</P>
<P>
Turkey is one of the few Middle East countries that has been on
good terms with the Jewish state which has angered the whole Arab
world for bringing the Middle East peace process to a stop through
its various anti-Arab policies since the right-wing Likud party
took power in the country last year. 
