<P>
MANILA, August 18 (Xinhua) -- Philippine President Fidel Ramos
today conveyed sympathies to the Hong Kong Special Administrative
Region (HKSAR) for the death of seven Hong Kong tourists who
perished in the boat capsize off Manila Bay last Friday.
</P>
