<HEADLINE> AIDS Cases Rise at Alarming Rate in Vietnam </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
HANOI, August 18 (Xinhua) -- The number of AIDS patients and
HIV carriers in Vietnam is rising at an alarming rate, causing
great concern to the Vietnamese government.
</P>
<P>
